<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1253182-how-can-this-book-have-2-stars-if-it">How can this book have 2 stars if it hasn&#39;t even been published yet?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1253182'><a id="like_count_community_question_1253182" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1253182?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">44 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F36595101-fire-and-fury">like</a></span>

